Question: Explain how to reach your home without using any street names
Answer:
first walk along the road where you see the big u-turn intersection, make a u-turn and go along the street. you will see a popular students' food court and keep going. then you will see a Chinese restaurant. turn left at the intersection. keep walking till you see an indian restaurant. go down the hills and turn left again. walk down for two hundred meters. and a little red-surfaced apartment will be on your left. and that's where i live.